Assertions
1. Hard Assert or simply assert
2. Soft Assert 

you cannot apply assertions in before or after method 
it has to be in test cases 

Assert.assertTrue
Assert.assertEquals
Assert.assertNotEquals
Assert.assertFalse

SOFT ASSERT WILL GIVE YOU THE LOGICAL SEQUENCE